    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_fu",
      "speaker_name": "慕容复",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容博",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_mo_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "鸠摩智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来慕容先生乃大燕王孙，失敬，失敬！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鸠摩智点头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说到这里，突然间右手一翻，掌中已多了一柄晶光灿然的匕首，一挥手，将匕首插入身旁几上，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yuan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "萧远山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我儿，此人之意，倒似不假，你瞧如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "萧峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容博道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说到这里，想起当日雁门关外宋兵和辽兵相互打草谷的残酷情状，越说越响，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_fu",
      "speaker_name": "慕容复",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你躲在这里有多久了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_fu",
      "speaker_name": "慕容复",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我问你躲在这里，有多久了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你⋯⋯你⋯⋯你⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我佛慈悲，善哉，善哉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_mo_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "鸠摩智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是宝刹自己的事，外人如何得知？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "服事僧虽是少林寺僧人，但只剃度而不拜师、不传武功、不修禅定、不列",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老僧合什道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "群僧一齐合掌道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老僧摇头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄因、玄生齐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 890,
      "line_end": 890
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yin",
      "speaker_name": "玄因",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无相劫指",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 894,
      "line_end": 894
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "双手拢在衣袖之中，暗暗使出",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 898,
      "line_end": 898
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_mo_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "鸠摩智",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小无相功",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 916,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "虚竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "便道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 920,
      "line_end": 920
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鸠摩智心道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 926,
      "line_end": 926
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "微微一笑，也不点破。那老僧续道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 928,
      "line_end": 928
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_seng",
      "speaker_name": "那老僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "次序颠倒，大难已在旦夕之间",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 940,
      "line_end": 940
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧远山全身一凛，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 950,
      "line_end": 950
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yuan_shan",
      "speaker_name": "萧远山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老僧又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 950,
      "line_end": 950
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧远山更是惊讶，颤声道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 952,
      "line_end": 952
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧峰大喜，磕了两个头，这才站起。那老僧叹了口气，说道：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 962,
      "line_end": 962
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老僧摇头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 968,
      "line_end": 968
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伸手携住慕容博右手，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1000,
      "line_end": 1000
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_seng",
      "speaker_name": "那老僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你竟忍心如此，让令尊受此彻骨奇痛的煎熬？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1002,
      "line_end": 1002
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容复气往上冲，喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1008,
      "line_end": 1008
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧峰更不打话，呼的一掌，一招降龙廿八掌中的",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1010,
      "line_end": 1010
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_fu",
      "speaker_name": "慕容复",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "斗转星移",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1014,
      "line_end": 1014
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容复喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1046,
      "line_end": 1046
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_fu",
      "speaker_name": "慕容复",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧远山咬牙切齿的道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1046,
      "line_end": 1046
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老僧道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1048,
      "line_end": 1048
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧远山道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1050,
      "line_end": 1050
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_seng",
      "speaker_name": "那老僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_bo",
      "speaker_name": "慕容博",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "百会穴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1062,
      "line_end": 1062
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_fu",
      "speaker_name": "慕容复",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹，爹爹！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1066,
      "line_end": 1066
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_seng",
      "speaker_name": "那老僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧老施主，你要去那里，这就请便。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1120,
      "line_end": 1120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老僧道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1122,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧远山道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1124,
      "line_end": 1124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那老僧点头道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1126,
      "line_end": 1126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叹了口气，说道：",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1132,
      "line_end": 1132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧峰叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1134,
      "line_end": 1134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_seng",
      "speaker_name": "那老僧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好俊的功夫！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 1156,
      "line_end": 1156
    },
